      <title>美国联邦贸易委员会启动对微软的反垄断调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-28/ftc-opens-microsoft-antitrust-investigation-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦贸易委员会已对微软展开反垄断调查，调查范围从该公司的云计算和软件许可业务到网络安全产品和人工智能产品等方方面面。Josh Sisco 报道了《彭博社：亚洲贸易》。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-28/ftc-opens-microsoft-antitrust-investigation-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 01:23:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国电动汽车热潮或将导致汽油需求下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/china-s-ev-boom-threatens-to-push-gasoline-demand-off-a-cliff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从北京故宫周围古巷里的特斯拉充电桩，到西部沙漠中设有充电桩的偏僻高速公路休息站，中国运输车辆电气化 — — 和汽油消亡 — — 的迹象随处可见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/china-s-ev-boom-threatens-to-push-gasoline-demand-off-a-cliff</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 01:05:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
