    <item>
      <title>特朗普最新言论引发墨西哥谈判 比索暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/trump-triggers-peso-whiplash-with-latest-post-on-mexico-talk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他与墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆进行了非常富有成效的会谈，墨西哥比索随即上涨，缩减了本周早些时候的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/trump-triggers-peso-whiplash-with-latest-post-on-mexico-talk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 00:54:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗原油出口放缓，中国买家抢购未售出石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/chinese-buyers-soak-up-unsold-oil-as-iranian-crude-flows-slow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国制裁扩大，伊朗石油供应仍然比平时更少，价格也更昂贵，中国的独立炼油商纷纷从中东和非洲各地抢购石油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/chinese-buyers-soak-up-unsold-oil-as-iranian-crude-flows-slow</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 00:45:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
